            "data": {
                "title": "Usual Suspects | 2022-2024",
                "subtitle": "It's Only Money was made by only 5 full-time devs including myself, because of that you'll see that I managed to get my hands into a lot aspects of the game. During my time with Usual Suspects I was able to push myself much further not just in terms of UI/UX design but also getting a greater understanding of UMG, Materials and programming with Blueprint in Unreal Engine. All of the UI here was created, implemented and mostly programmed by myself from start to finish. ",
